Zhongxin Fruits might have a move sooner than later. Can watch for this one. Trading Game plan: Cup & Handle rally  test year high of $0.037 and break out into 4 series. Have been watching this one and it is indeed controlled nicely by BBs (remember the gap up 4 pips on 11th Nov to $0.036  done by BBs and yesterday T+4 from the highlighted volume spike  hence main selling pressure over) Also  yesterday at closing  the BBs was matching 100 shares at 0.034 where there was 50 lots in sell Q. However  at the final second  they removed 50 lots sell Q 34 and closed it $0.035. This shows the BBs intention for higher prices with such control . If trade  do have a stop loss plan too. Good luck to all vested.
